3. Desktop Wallet kya hota hai?
Ye wallet app hota hai jo:
Windows / Linux / macOS pe install hota hai
Computer me locally run hota hai
Usually non-custodial hota hai

Private keys can be exported

Private keys ya seed phrase tumhare system me store hoti hai
Tum backup le sakti ho
Tum control me ho
Ye non-custodial wallet category me aata hai.

